data.description: Take in this amazing 6 bedroom, 3 bath, 2 car garage home located in the coveted Woodland Hills Estates. This 3,576 sq. ft., home sits on a fantastic .73 corner lot with room for everyone & everything. Main level boasts an open floorplan with a large appointed kitchen as the center, custom cabinetry, extensive breakfast bar & counterspace, & a large walk-in pantry. The light filled, oversized living room is a perfect spot to gather and relax in front of the gorgeous gas fireplace, while the dining room has a lovely picture window and is adorned with a wood burning stove. The main floor consists of four bedrooms, with two wings, each containing two bedrooms and a bathroom. There is a luxurious sauna that is accessible through one of the bathrooms and can also be entered from the 20x12 Trex deck, which is the perfect spot for your hot tub and grill. The downstairs area includes two bedrooms, a bathroom, and a family room and has its own entry...AirBnB anyone?  The right side ...
